https://azure.microsoft.com/en-in/services/
The core capabilities in Azure Bastion include
	1.RDP and SSH from the Azure Portal
	2.Remote session over SSL and firewall traversal for RDP/SSH
	3.No public IP address required on Azure Virtual Machines
	4.Simplified secure rules management
Azure Virtual Machine Serial Console
	1.The serial console can only be accessed by using the 
	  Azure portal and is allowed only for those users who 
	  have an access role of Contributor or higher to the
	  VM or virtual machine scale set.
	
